    "description": "The Warehouse Shipment Dispatch API facilitates the efficient management and processing of outbound shipment manifests by integrating with carrier services. This API allows users to dispatch items from a warehouse, ensuring streamlined logistics and real-time tracking of shipments. Utilize this service to enhance operational efficiency and improve delivery times.",
