        "description": "This operation initiates the dispatch process for an outbound shipment manifest associated with a specific carrier from the warehouse. It expects details about the shipment in the request body, including relevant identifiers and authorization information. The outcome is a successful dispatch confirmation, provided the inputs are valid and the request is correctly authorized.",
